{"tid":1816290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"七個月了 大家仲記唔唔記得點解我地要割美心？","createTime":"2020-01-08T06:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T15:51:10.000Z","uid":197568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fbfd8f7f98dc8eeb53b229fa2880cffb99ed295c","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"見到身邊嘅人戒美心戒到如火如荼 搞到人生好似要飲水維生咁<br />\n但原來 冇乜人記得當初點解要割<br />\n有日問某朋友 其實點解要裝修美心？<br />\n佢地答 唔係中資咩？<br />\n再望一望Starbucks門口 紅卜卜大大隻字寫中資<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但上網睇一睇<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美心唔係中資啊</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（根據wiki）</span><br />\n美心嘅股份喺由牛奶國際同香港食品平均持有<br />\n其中 前者係英資 屬怡和集團旗下 後者則由伍舜德同伍沾德家族為最大股東<br />\n<br />\n所以 唔好再話美心係中資<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁樣係抹殺咗佢本身做過嘅仆街嘢啊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n美心係衰喺伍淑清同牛奶國際手上<br />\n<br />\n個八婆得零點幾幾幾個%股份係到扮大袋我當佢維園呀伯講廢話<br />\n<br />\n但牛奶國際不打自招向狗交cctv<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕！對！唔！可！以！原！諒！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實呢個只係其中一個例子 點解割美心呢啲好小事 但重要嘅係個mindset<br />\n<br />\n半年發生咗太多事 我地有太多嘢要記<br />\n但都唔好畀籍口自己善忘 <br />\n<br />\n點解當初要企出尼 點解和理平開始撐勇武 點解和理非都升級變勇武 點解撤回都要繼續抗爭 點解要攬炒 721 831 101 雙11 仲有更多不能盡錄 但全部我地都要記得一清二楚<br />\n<br />\n依家全世界都有三毛 有fake news 有鬼 有人捉鬼<br />\n所以我地要更加用力記住自己為咗乜嘢而行動<br />\n<br />\n唔肯定美心係咪中資 咁就去查 唔好人云亦云 唔好憑自己biased嘅記憶然後鳩嗡 一個人頭腦清醒冇用 要大家一齊清醒先可以集思廣益 先冇咁易畀人帶到風向<br />\n<br />\n咁先係將抗爭融入生活<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人 一齊繼續加油<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"2bc017f178cc01339c27c9649364f128a6d409a4","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:49:00.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"31272577f963001da82acb4b52704b5cb3ea56ff","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7e04e6ea18a74e3e776e681f9946d2a1c6662cce","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:49:22.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"f254a5e49ec73e5112afda429d2ca854f2f628fe","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:49:35.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"7cad076be016cb028154bb7cc800b1c735e48a19","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:49:48.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"ae8895e0298f69606f7da62f71c0b51f4b15ba57","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"25f3b371e54db8720fc26a79009cdfa1647b2fa2","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:50:18.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"b3cf3d9cbace76d87e8df677577bc021e2f22a71","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"36c3077c5f2284d94671f5b2d19ea257f13ca97e","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"368a7c63bf522370c89727882aa8ad21b696d520","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:51:03.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"64d0120c66d1b823af1cf5b1b4c1882a9d6f9019","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7027f42ee44f1e44d5be1af6c0c1a6edc51a9341","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3774d39c824da2768400fc2c8f5a9772ed99842c","tid":1816290,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply